                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Smite Corpus",
                  "pageId": 116683,
                  "revisionId": 2687264,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example, if you had a Riven Mod with x0.5 Damage to Corpus and a max rank Smite Corpus with x1.3 Damage to Corpus, you would have a 1 - 0.5 + 0.3 = x0.8 multiplier for damage against Corpus with both mods equipped."
                }
